verse.name: v1a
verse.lines:
Open Up!
Let it Flow Now
Open Up!

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Out of the Mundane
To where I’m Ordained
For things that were made
Were made from things Unseen
There are Realms of Glory
For my world to see
Dimensions found only
In Jesus Christ the Son

verse.name: v1b
verse.lines:
Channels of my Spirit, Open Up!
I am with the Father, Open Up!
No Boundaries No Limits, Open Up!
Let Deep call unto Deep,
Open Up!
Channels of my Spirit, Open Up!

Let Deep call unto Deep,
Open Up!
